00:00:11,891 --> 00:00:13,661
Slammin' kicks.

3
00:00:13,761 --> 00:00:15,632
Is that kid wearing Slipremes?

4
00:00:15,732 --> 00:00:18,136
He totally is.

5
00:00:19,205 --> 00:00:22,111
These are my first tie-shoes.

6
00:00:22,177 --> 00:00:24,248
You're wearing
the new Slipreme Caliphates?

7
00:00:24,315 --> 00:00:27,321
How did a chum-wad like you
get a pair?

8
00:00:27,388 --> 00:00:29,258
My daddy took my cat
to the cat doctor,

9
00:00:29,325 --> 00:00:30,962
and when Daddy came home,

10
00:00:31,029 --> 00:00:33,066
